				<h1> What is Self Care? </h1>
				<blockquote>"The right and responsibility to take care of your physical, emotional, and spiritual well-being."- Pauline Salvucci</blockquote> 
				<img class='img-circle img-responsive' id='desk' src='http://graphics8.nytimes.com/images/2013/09/22/magazine/22well/22well-superJumbo-v2.jpg'/>
